
Severs
======
watcher - used in devserver mode to auto refresh all attached clients.
static  - server static files in devmode; optionally production
wsgi    - (Web Server Gateway Interface) application server (you main server if you choose)

Directories
===========
configure  - json configuration for servers
library    - vendor code and other chuncks of functionality
servers    - node servers including watcher, wsgi and static
static     - all media files to be servered css, images, js, media, flash
templates  - files to be rendered by template engine and delivered by wsgi
utility    - scripts and tools, some will compress and distribute static content

